<title>lyst trnymty</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 lyst trnymty rby swy̱ lḥn wklmạt
 flys fyhạ qwh wlys mnhạ brkạt
 ạ̹lạ ạ̹dẖạ brwḥk wsẖkẖṣk ạlsạmy
 tbạrk trnymty wạlʿzf wạltsbyḥ
 (ạ̉skb mn rwḥk ʿly̱ trnymty)2
 ạ̉skb mn rwḥk rby
 fhy klạm mn ạ̹nsạn qd ml smʿh ạlbsẖr
 wlḥn kbạqy ạlạlḥạn lys lh ạ̉y ạ̉tẖr
 ạ̹lạ ạ̹dẖạ jmlthạ bsẖkẖṣk ạlsạmy
 kllthạ jllthạ jʿlthạ tsbyḥ</lyrics>
